products.title: Nike
products.description: From workouts to getting to work, the Nike Backpack has you covered. A large zipped compartment offers room for shoes or an extra set of clothes for the gym and your books and laptop for school. 2 exterior pockets help keep electronics and small essentials organised and stored securely. This product is made from at least 65% recycled polyester fibres.

products.title: Jordan Icon
products.description: This backpack has an elevated look making it great for everyday wear. It's made from durable poly fabric and features the iconic elephant skin pattern to complement your Jordans. The spacious main compartment houses a padded laptop sleeve, the zip pocket on the front helps secure small items you want quick and easy access to and the adjustable straps provide comfortable wear.

products.title: Nike Utility Speed 2.0
products.description: Keep your gear organised with exterior zipped front pockets for small items and a spacious main compartment with a luggage-style zip that opens fully to the bottom. The main compartment fits a pair of shoes and a change of clothes and has internal slip pockets as well as dedicated pockets for a 16 inch laptop and other small electronics.

products.title: Nike Brasilia
products.description: You've got stuff and we've got the perfect way to carry it all. Meet the Nike Brasilia backpack. Its roomy main compartment has space for books and other large gear, while the mesh side pockets can fit a water bottle or other small items you want to keep within easy reach.

products.title: Nike Pro
products.description: Wet weather doesn't have to be a pain in the back. Nike Storm-FIT technology helps resist elements like wind and water to help keep your stuff dry, while a double-zip main compartment with a laptop sleeve and a reflective-design front pocket help keep you organised.

products.title: Nike Utility Power
products.description: Your life isn't one-dimensional, so your bag shouldn't be either. Keep your work life separated from your play with separate internal compartments for your laptop, phone and shoes. There are also three exterior zip pockets for small essentials to help keep you organised.

products.title: Nike One
products.description: Don't tell your other bags, but this might just be the only one you need. A large main pocket and interior pockets make organising essentials a breeze. Padded and adjustable shoulder straps for comfortable carrying.

products.title: Nike Air
products.description: Keep your gear in check with a backpack inspired by the iconic Air Max 95. With convenient organisation that includes a laptop sleeve and water bottle pouch, this backpack keeps up with you. Padded adjustable straps keep you comfortable whether you're headed to a kickabout or hanging out with friends.

products.title: Nike Academy Team
products.description: The Nike Academy Team Backpack gives you spacious storage with multiple pockets. Padding on the straps and back panel lets you comfortably carry your gear.

products.title: Nike Sportswear RPM
products.description: Meet the backpack made for the person who needs to carry it all. Whether it's on a sunny-day hike or hiking around campus, you have plenty of space to stay organised while also staying comfortable. Multiple zip pockets complement the spacious main compartment, while both the back and straps are padded for long days on your feet.

products.title: Nike Heritage
products.description: Take your gear to go with the Nike Heritage Backpack. Its spacious main compartment features a sleeve that holds up to a 15 inch laptop, so your computer is never out of reach. 2 zipped accessories pockets help keep your gear organised and easy to grab. This product is made from at least 65% recycled polyester fibres.

products.title: Nike Academy Team
products.description: The weather doesn't keep you from training, and it shouldn't keep you from having dry gear. Whether resting on the ground or hanging on a fence, this backpack handles less-than-ideal game and training conditions—and holds your ball in the front pocket. The rain fly features Nike Storm-FIT technology to help provide extra coverage from the elements, while mesh on the bag allows breathability and ventilation on those good-weather days.

products.title: Jordan Alpha
products.description: This backpack is for those who are self-assured, confident, powerful. It's made from durable recycled fabrics and has a versatile design that will take you from work to gym and to travel. The spacious main compartment has a 2-way zip closure and houses a laptop compartment, as well as a mesh slip pocket to secure smaller items. A front zip pocket helps secure smaller items you want quick and easy access to, pockets on the sides can be used to hold your favourite beverages and a zip shoe garage at the bottom allows you to easily bring an extra pair of shoes for travel or keep gym shoes away from the items you want to keep from getting soiled.

products.title: Nike Aura
products.description: Keep your essentials close and your style game on point. A 24-litre capacity makes this bag ideal for carrying nearly everything you need for your day. A front zip pocket is perfect for smaller essentials while an interior slip pocket fits most laptops.
